---
title: Cranberry-Thyme Roasted Chicken with Potato Pancakes, Harvest Salad & Chive Sour Cream
description: What time is it? Cranberry thyme! This delectable dinner stars a tantalizing mix of cranberry jam, red wine vinegar, and thyme swirled into a tangy-sweet sauce for roasted chicken. Crispy potato pancakes, paired with a chive sour cream dipper, make the ideal side dish. And while all of that would be perfectly delicious on its own, you’ll take it over the top with a harvest salad tossed with apple, white cheddar, and pecans. Yep, going the extra mile is just your style.
